io.github.zachohara.bukkit.common.command

Class CommandRulesEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.zachohara.bukkit.common.command.CommandRulesEntry

  • public class CommandRulesEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    A CommandRulesEntry object represents the rules and conditions for a command. All of the conditions outlined in this object need to be verified before attempting to execute the command.

    This class contians rules for a command such as minimum and maximum expected amounts of arguments, the required permissions and conditions of any entity trying to use the command, and the type(s) of players that can be targeted by the command under certain situations.

    Author:
    Zach Ohara
